                    <b>How to install this application</b>
                    <br>
                    <p>Here you will learn how to get started..</p>
                    <p>This application depends on Nodejs and Mongodb</p>
                    <p>So please make sure you have Nodejs installed on your machine before opening this application</p>
                    <p>To install Nodejs go to <a href="#">Nodejs official website</a> Then download and install it.</p>
                    <p>if you need to help for download and install Nodejs please watch this video => <a href="#">How to
                            download and install Nodejs</a></p>
                    <p>Now you can check if Nodejs is installed on your machine by adding this command in terminal</p>
                    <code>node --version</code>
                    <p>if you see the version of Nodejs thats mean everything is fine</p>
                    <p>Now check if NPM installed</p>
                    <code>npm --version</code>
                    <p>(don't worry, NPM will be installed with Nodejs by default)</p>
                    <p>Then you need to install Mongodb on your machine</p>
                    <p>if wou need help How to download and install Mongodb please click here to read more about this <a
                            href="#">How to download and install Mongodb</a></p>

                </div>
