                    <code><span class="uri">URI</span>=mongodb://localhost/shortUrl</code>
                    <p>When you ready to deploy your application please uncomment <span class="file">.env</span> file in
                        <span class="file">.gitignore</span> file, just remove # before <span class="file">.env</span>
                    </p>

                    <p>You can change local DB with real online mongoDB server</p>
